name: Pimpyaml-container
body: Pimpyaml is a simple configuration package for Pimple container. It implements `[ContainerInterface]`(https://github.com/container-interop/container-interop), so you can switch easly with another [container](https://github.com/container-interop/container-interop#projects-implementing-containerinterface)
